freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Went to doctor for the second time with a painful preauricular lymph node. Pain  started 3 hours after 2nd vaccine

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Pain and discomfort from a swollen preauricular lymph node by my ear. That I started feeling hours after receiving the second dose.
My Preauricular lymph node on right side has become painful and swollen

Still have a swollen lymph node but its getting better each day.
